data.description: Affordable Bath Co living. Open the door to your dreams of a massive 4 bedroom rancher on half basement. This home features 3 larger bedrooms and full bath on one end and on the other is a mind blowing Master Suite! The kitchen has new, warm wood cabinets, and high-end appliances waiting for you. Now, step into the Master suite with a light filled living space leading you to french doors which enclose the Master bedroom, bath and walk-in closet. You also have main level laundry and basement access right off the kitchen. All of this is centrally located to the 2 car garage with access from the kitchen. Recent updates include flooring, kitchen and HVAC.  Sit on your front porch, grab a hot coffee and watch the sunrise or catch the lazy afternoon shadows from your back deck. The lot has mature trees and is fenced for your fur babies or other little angels.  This home sits high upon a hill overlooking Bath County High School, and the Hot Springs Valley. You are just minutes from the famed Homestead Resort, Jefferson Pools, and a short drive to Lake Moomaw and the Cascades golf course. Affordability is key in this area so call your agent today and schedule your private tour!
